OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with often large amounts of
OL,6,Fcloud. Some brightness is also likely,
OL,7,Fespecially across Norfolk, but showers
OL,8,Fmay develop here later. A spell of
OL,9,Fmorning rain, perhaps heavy, is
OL,10,Fpossible across Essex and southern
OL,11,FSuffolk. Feeling warm by afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny evening showers, mainly
OL,14,Faffecting north-western areas soon
OL,15,Ffading then a dry night with some
OL,16,Fcloud breaks and light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
