OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FWednesday generally dry and
OL,6,Fbright, with some sunny spells likely
OL,7,Facross the region. Light winds
OL,8,Ffreshening a little in afternoon.
OL,9,FPatchy rain overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FCloud
OL,12,Fand showery rain clearing Thursday
OL,13,Fmorning, then bright, Friday and
OL,14,FSaturday likely to remain mostly dry
OL,15,Fand breezy, with clear or sunny
OL,16,Fspells. Temperatures mostly above
OL,17,Faverage throughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
